  "id": "api/core/Pipe",
  "title": "Pipe",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/Pipe\", \"name\": \"Pipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L629-L630\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L629-L630\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"pipe\">Pipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#pipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Decorator that marks a class as pipe and supplies configuration metadata.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/Pipe#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  \n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>Option</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#name\">\n          <code>name</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td><p>The pipe name to use in template bindings.</p>\n</td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#pure\">\n          <code>pure</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td><p>When true, the pipe is pure, meaning that the\n<code>transform()</code> method is invoked only when its input arguments\nchange. Pipes are pure by default.</p>\n</td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>A pipe class must implement the <code><a href=\"api/core/PipeTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">PipeTransform</a></code> interface.\nFor example, if the name is \"myPipe\", use a template binding expression\nsuch as the following:</p>\n<code-example>\n{{ exp | myPipe }}\n</code-example>\n<p>The result of the expression is passed to the pipe's <code>transform()</code> method.</p>\n<p>A pipe must belong to an NgModule in order for it to be available\nto a template. To make it a member of an NgModule,\nlist it in the <code>declarations</code> field of the <code><a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> metadata.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">Options<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"name\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead><tr><th>\n      <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n        <h3 id=\"name\">name<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#name\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L605-L609\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L605-L609\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>The pipe name to use in template bindings.</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n          name: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n  <a id=\"pure\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead><tr><th>\n      <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n        <h3 id=\"pure\">pure<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#pure\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L610-L621\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L610-L621\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>When true, the pipe is pure, meaning that the\n<code>transform()</code> method is invoked only when its input arguments\nchange. Pipes are pure by default.</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n          pure: boolean\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>If the pipe has internal state (that is, the result\ndepends on state other than its arguments), set <code>pure</code> to false.\nIn this case, the pipe is invoked on each change-detection cycle,\neven if the arguments have not changed.</p>\n\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - api/core/WrappedValue\n - api/core/testing/TestBed\n - api/core/testing/TestBedStatic\n - guide/aot-compiler\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/Pipe#description\n - api/core/Pipe#name\n - api/core/Pipe#options\n - api/core/Pipe#pipe\n - api/core/Pipe#pure\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L605-L609\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L610-L621\n - ht